---
title: Chicken & Sweetcorn Soup with Roasted Veggies & Spring Onion
description: Summer and winter collide in the pan tonight to transform soup into a breezy new dinner sensation. Fresh and warm chicken is cooked up to perfection with vibrant corn alongside warm and cosy veggies like carrot and potato in a broth that balances everything. It’s the season of soup for sure!

*Unfortunately, this
week's celery was in short
supply, so we've replaced
it with leek. Don't worry,
the recipe will be just as
delicious, just be sure to
follow your recipe card!*
